Peanut Butter Chocolate cake . 
@skippysingapore really goes well with cake. 
Staying home and bake this cake over the weekend. Super satisfied with the texture and flavour esp with peanut butter added . So damn good 😋. .
.
. [Promo] 
RedMart X Skippy !!!
Buy 2 bottles of 500g for $11.90 during 13-19 May .
.
Ingredients
* 	80g salted butter
* 	50g granulated sugar
* 	20g packed light brown sugar
* 	1 large eggs
* 	1/4 teaspoon vanilla extract
* 	40g all-purpose flour * 	6g dark cocoa powder
* 	1/4 teaspoon salt
* 
Peanut Butter Filling
* 	60g Skippy creamy peanut butter
* 	10g salted butter .
.
.
.
